<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>turn on the waterworks • turn someone’s water off </xh5><p> <i>turn on the waterworks</i>—(coll.) begin to cry <i>(also: turn on the water tap):</i> Sally <u>turned on the waterworks</u> when she got yelled at.</p><p> <i>turn someone’s water off</i>—(coll.) make a person appear more modest <i>(usually of smb. who is acting too arrogant):</i> It took a scolding from the coach to <u>turn Tom’s water off</u>.</p> </entry>
